wiki/Moi_Ren%C3%A9e","retrieved":1775976718875},{"title":"Commonwealth MRT station (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Commonwealth_MRT_station\" title=\"Commonwealth MRT station\">Commonwealth MRT station</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\">'s</span> platform columns have been compared to the columns in <a href=\"/wiki/Shophouse#Singapore_shophouses\" title=\"Shophouse\">Singapore shophouses</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Commonwealth_MRT_station","retrieved":1775976718880},{"title":"Saint Monegundis (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Monegundis\" title=\"Monegundis\">Saint Monegundis</a></b> left her husband and became an <a href=\"/wiki/Anchorite\" title=\"Anchorite\">anchorite</a> after the deaths of her two daughters?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monegundis","retrieved":1775976718880},{"title":"HiAnime (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the pirate anime streaming site <b><a href=\"/wiki/HiAnime\" title=\"HiAnime\">HiAnime</a></b> had more visitors than legal competitors like Crunchyroll or Disney+?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HiAnime","retrieved":1775976718881},{"title":"Mingering Mike (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Mingering_Mike\" title=\"Mingering Mike\">Mingering Mike</a></b> spent nearly a decade creating a fictional music career complete with albums, singles, and record labels?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mingering_Mike","retrieved":1775976718885},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r4523569\" typeof=\"mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion\" about=\"#mwt8\" data-mw=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;templatestyles&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;Banner/styles.css&quot;},&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner